results.name: Al Najada Doha Hotel by Tivoli

properties.description: Set 13 km from Hamad International Airport, this luxury hotel with a grand exterior is a 9-minute walk from the bustling Souq Waqif and 2 km from the National Museum of Qatar. Upscale rooms with warm furnishings offer free Wi-Fi, flat-screen TVs and coffeemakers, plus city views. Sophisticated 1- to 3-bedroom suites add terraces and lounge areas; some have kitchenettes and dining rooms. There's an outdoor pool, a fitness center and a spa. Other amenities include a refined restaurant, a cafe and a pool bar, plus a business center and a banquet hall.

results.name: Wyndham Doha West Bay

properties.description: Set 19 km from Hamad International Airport, this upscale high-rise hotel with Gulf views is opposite The Gate Mall and 7 km from the Museum of Islamic Art. Refined rooms with chic furnishings offer free Wi-Fi, flat-screen TVs and safes; some include minibars and/or kitchenettes. Sophisticated 1-to 3-bedroom apartments with floor-to-ceiling windows feature lounge and dining areas, washer/dryers, and city and/or Gulf views. Room service is available 24/7. Valet parking is complimentary. There are 3 restaurants, 2 cafes and a lounge, plus 2 pools (1 indoor), and a spa with a gym. There are also conference facilities and multiple event spaces.

Room service is available. There's a chic restaurant and a cafe, as well as a lobby lounge and a terrace. Other amenities include an indoor pool, a gym, a steam room and a sauna. Breakfast and parking are available.
